      "text": "I do agree with the notion that a blog is a stream and it is definitely serialized, reverse chronologically. However, for me the key difference is not that serial versus random like nature of access. Instead, the key difference is that a stream is more ephemeral. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
