    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "835a317c8cd4f057",
      "text": "However, I will offer up an observation. The ability to directly edit what you write directly where it is published, such as with Federated Wiki and how Dave's [http://scripting.com/davenet/1999/12/08/editthispagecom.html EditThisPage] worked is more conducive to gardening than the separate writing and publishing models of most blogging platforms like WordPress and micro.blog. "
    },
